{"tid":762162,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食咗廿年大家樂終於中返次頭獎","createTime":"2018-07-31T04:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T05:44:59.000Z","uid":195887,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bff9eee09f72ac987a194a072badfcb7d508420d","tid":762162,"uid":195887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:51:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 小弟樓下得大家樂一間野食，成日都要被迫幫襯。 但係今日發生咗件事就係阿姐汁錯餐。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一開始叫咗個外賣喱腩飯(值$49蚊左右)，個飯其實只係值錢在啲牛身上。 當我拎咗個外賣返屋企打開，發現個白飯底變左做鮑片炒飯(值$35蚊)。 我用49蚊就食到80蚊野，感覺非常high&amp;食到lamlamlee。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知有無巴絲試過餐廳汁錯餐而著數咗呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adb7fdf64348a8437c3df069d109ec71ac815c9","tid":762162,"uid":180035,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"叫炸雞翼飯 返到屋企一開冇雞翼 得飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e708aaa29b0e3a15ae8c10954c6e4bdaf5cf36dc","tid":762162,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0634d0449c71927ff9cbe895d7ca22cef22b0ea2","tid":762162,"uid":33875,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:54:31.000Z","msg":"出去搵下食咗盒白飯嗰個Post"},{"pid":"3f75523cd03bf1112b708c236202020ee03d2d3d","tid":762162,"uid":195887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8adb7fdf64348a8437c3df069d109ec71ac815c9","tid":762162,"uid":180035,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"叫炸雞翼飯 返到屋企一開冇雞翼 得飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b870ce42b407c423eb564f5e